name: SEQUOIAMOVIEZONE
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sequoia movie zone
des: This skill will give you a brief idea on any movie you asked for. You can start by saying "Alexa start sequoia movie zone ". You will get a welcome message and will ask for a movie name. You can say any movie name as you wish for. Then alexa will respond with a brief description on that movie covering all important aspects.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
